# Rock, Paper, Scissors â€“ Python Game ðŸŽ®

A simple command-line Rock, Paper, Scissors game written in Python. Play against the computer in a best-of-three match and see who comes out on top!

---

##  Game Description

This game lets a user play **Rock, Paper, Scissors** against the computer. The match is best-of-three rounds. The scores are tracked and an overall winner is announced at the end.

---

##  How to Run

1. **Clone the repo or download the file:**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/rock-paper-scissors.git
cd rock-paper-scissors

## Run the Game

```bash
python rockerpaperscissors.py
Make sure Python is installed on your system (python --version to check)


